OL,3,C'It's our lifeline': Deaf and blind
OL,4,Ccentre at risk of closure
OL,6,FAn urgent fundraising appeal has been
OL,7,Flaunched to save a centre which
OL,8,Fprovides vital services for deaf and
OL,9,Fblind people from closure.
OL,11,FThe Leeds Society for Deaf and Blind
OL,12,FPeople said it needs to raise #100,000
OL,13,Fto keep its community centre open,
OL,14,Fwhich provides access to education,
OL,15,Finformation and booking British Sign
OL,16,FLanguage interpreters.
