OL,3,C'It's our lifeline': Deaf and blind
OL,4,Ccentre at risk of closure
OL,6,FDeaf Club member Alison Spear said:
OL,7,F"Where would I meet my friends if it
OL,8,Fdisappeared? Who would I talk to?
OL,9,FThere would be nothing. I would be
OL,10,Fstuck at home which wouldn't be very
OL,11,Fgood for my mental health at all. It
OL,12,Fmust stay open."
OL,14,FA GoFundMe fundraiser has been set up
OL,15,Fto try and raise funds.
